Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.13,0:04:01.51,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}To sink or swim {\fsp1}生き残るために
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.51,0:04:04.01,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}dog eat dog world {\fsp1}だと言い聞かせ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.01,0:04:08.89,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}What went wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.89,0:04:11.81,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Survival of the fittest {\fsp1}弱肉強食
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.81,0:04:13.64,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}If it's the world that our wisdom will lead
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.64,0:04:18.82,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Then tell me what went wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.82,0:04:21.36,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}I've paid my dues
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.36,0:04:23.15,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}I've sold my soul
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.15,0:04:27.03,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}So tell me, what is left for me
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.03,0:04:29.20,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}when I've given up everything
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.20,0:04:32.75,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fsp1}ねぇ　どう描いてたんだろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.75,0:04:39.25,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fsp1}どの景色を見ても　何も感じなくなったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.25,0:04:42.84,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fsp1}ねぇ　考え直しても
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.84,0:04:49.51,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fsp1}あの景色を求めていた　僕は今無感情なの？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.51,0:04:52.93,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fsp1}ねぇ　どう描いてたんだろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.93,0:04:59.52,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fsp1}どの景色を見ても　何も感じなくなったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.52,0:05:03.03,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fsp1}ねぇ　考え直しても
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.03,0:05:09.62,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fsp1}あの景色を求めていた　僕は今無感情なの？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.62,0:05:12.16,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fsp1}真実の見えない世界
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.16,0:05:14.66,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fsp1}善と悪のバランスを保ち
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.66,0:05:17.17,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fsp1}殺すか殺されるかの
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.17,0:05:19.71,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fsp1}ちっぽけな世界なのかよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.71,0:05:25.55,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fsp1}おい　誰か答えてみてくれよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.55,0:05:27.55,op-jp,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.13,0:04:01.51,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是沉是浮 为了生存
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.51,0:04:04.01,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}告诉他 这是同类相残的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.01,0:04:08.89,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为什么会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.89,0:04:11.81,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2)}适者生存 弱肉强食
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.81,0:04:13.64,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果智慧能引领这世界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.64,0:04:18.82,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那就告诉我 为什么会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.82,0:04:21.36,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我已付出太多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.36,0:04:23.15,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我已出卖灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.15,0:04:27.03,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}告诉我 如果我放弃一切
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.03,0:04:29.20,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}又能够得到些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.20,0:04:32.75,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}回答我 这是个怎样的世界？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.75,0:04:39.25,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我看过太多风景 却毫无感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.25,0:04:42.84,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}回答我 我已思考无数次
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.84,0:04:49.51,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为了追寻那个风景 我是否已毫无感情？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.51,0:04:52.93,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}回答我 这是个怎样的世界？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.93,0:04:59.52,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我看过太多风景 却毫无感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.52,0:05:03.03,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}回答我 我已思考无数次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.03,0:05:09.62,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为了追寻那个风景 我是否已毫无感情？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.62,0:05:12.16,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}看不见真相的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.16,0:05:14.66,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}维持善恶的平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.66,0:05:17.17,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}杀或被杀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.17,0:05:19.71,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这世界难道这么无趣吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.71,0:05:25.55,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喂 谁能回答我啊
